# Presentation layer

- Location: `lib/features/<feature>/presentation/` or `lib/features/components/<name>/presentation/`
- Pages: `<name>_page.dart`. Components: `<name>_component.dart`.
- Use `MultiBlocProvider` with typed `providers` list.
- Import shared states from `lib/widgets/common/` (LoadingWidget, ErrorWidget, UnknownStateWidget).
- Map failures via `ErrorLocalizer` from `lib/core/errors/error_localizer.dart`.
- New routes: update `lib/router.dart` (prefer `integration-wiring` subagent).
